New! Thanks to your feedback we have added the ability for the app to keep you logged in. Log in with your username and password, check the “Enable touch ID to sign in” box and stay logged in for up to 30 days.

Terms and conditions for the My CT 'Money' Program have been updated.

Bug fixes and app enhancements.

We appreciate your feedback! Email us at customerservice@cantire.com

In this version of the app we’ve added support for the WOW Guide (available April 11th). This exciting, digital companion to the WOW Guide includes the following:
• Digital WOW Guide – Find 200 additional pages packed with more products, ideas, galleries and how-tos.
• Hover & Discover – Scan every page and product in the WOW Guide to unlock exciting digital extras, how-tos, product videos, expert advice and a virtual reality patio builder.
• Pay & Pickup – See something in the guide you like? Just add to cart!

In our latest version of the app you can now search, select and buy from our large selection of Tires & Wheels in-app:
- Select your vehicle and add it to your garage. You can even upload pictures of your car(s) or truck(s)!
- Choose the correct tire and/or wheel sizes for your application, or create a complete package.
- Decide on the right tire for you with help from Canadian Tire’s test results.
- Add your selection of Tires & Wheels to your cart, pay in-app and pick them up at your favourite Canadian Tire Store!
